my_net_service_name= 
 (DESCRIPTION= 
   (ADDRESS=(some address here))
   (CONNECT_DATA= 
     (SID=some_SID_name)))

Where my_net_service_name string is what you have to subsitite for ENTRY_FROM_TNSNAMES from my Java example.

